    <h1>Hermes Hemmnis</h1>
    <p class="intro" onclick="openIntroCarousel()">
    Hermes Hemmnis is a Hamburg-based artist duo consisting of Till Knapp and Lennart Häusser, working at the intersection of <span class="kw">composition</span>, improvisation, and <span class="kw">sound research</span>. Their practice focuses on the transformation and recontextualization of recorded and live-generated material through the integration of <span class="kw">field recordings</span>, sampling, synthesis, and processed electric guitar. Rooted in spatial listening practices and site-specific approaches, their work extends to live soundtracks for film and collaborations with locally situated acoustic instruments. <span class="intro-arrow" onclick="openIntroCarousel()">→</span>

