        In 2023, we realized a site-specific concert at I Punkt Skateland, supported by the Claussen-Simon-Stiftung. The project focused on acoustic exploration as a means of creating immersive listening environments. Through the deliberate shaping of sonic space, layered sound structures emerged that invite alternative modes of spatial perception. The work engages with unconventional concert settings, integrating their specific conditions into the compositional process. In doing so, it examines established modes of listening and proposes a reconfiguration of spatial experience. <span class="intro-arrow" id="dot-skateland"><b>→</b></span>
