      <div class="overlay-header-body">
        In collaboration with Stockholm-based dancer and artist Frank Koenen, Hermes Hemmnis develop a shared performative practice rooted in an ongoing exchange between movement and sound. Each project begins with a concrete starting point – an object, a gesture, or an idea – proposed by Koenen, which serves as the foundation for a new composition. From this material, Hermes Hemmnis develop original music, to which Koenen in turn responds with a choreography. In performance, the music is always played live, creating a space in which sound and movement continuously inform and transform each other. <span class="intro-arrow" id="more-frank"><b>→</b></span>
