      <div class="release-body" id="body-oap">
        <div class="release-body-inner">
          <p class="release-desc">In August 2025 a new recording was created in a remote forest cabin in Sweden. It combines field recordings of the surroundings and interacting musicians with synthesizer sounds and processed acoustic guitar tones. The material, recorded using various specialized microphones and a four-track cassette recorder, a series of experimental compositions characterized by their multi-layered structure.</p>
